snippet.title: GUNCHO Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2736220/GUNCHO/
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/id6469145099
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tinytouchtales.guncho

In this small scale, turn based tactics game, you spin Guncho's revolver cylinder to keep his bullets aligned to enemies. Fight your way through randomly generated shootouts. Upgrade your bullets and use tactical abilities to defeat your foes. Ride your donkey and become the ultimate Pistolero.
